01:07:42.079 --> 01:07:44.885
However, I can answer one
question immediately,

01:07:44.885 --> 01:07:48.606
which is really implied by what
you are saying more than asked

01:07:48.606 --> 01:07:49.400
directly.
 

01:07:49.400 --> 01:07:52.000
Yes, Dante is a peace poet.
 

01:07:52.000 --> 01:07:55.139
I would say that with full
confidence,

01:07:55.139 --> 01:07:57.380
though we know Dante was so
polemical,

01:07:57.380 --> 01:08:00.137
kicks shades,
is angry, fights,

01:08:00.137 --> 01:08:05.099
and there's always competing
visions in relation to the

01:08:05.099 --> 01:08:08.510
tradition and others,
but he's--Fundamentally,

01:08:08.510 --> 01:08:11.250
you have to establish,
you would say, differences;

01:08:11.250 --> 01:08:14.000
not really renounce your
differences,

01:08:14.000 --> 01:08:16.930
but actually make those
differences the orchestration,

01:08:16.930 --> 01:08:20.476
the musical orchestration that
is going on in Cantos XV,

01:08:20.476 --> 01:08:21.510
XVI, and XVII.
 

01:08:21.510 --> 01:08:22.710
This is the heaven of music.
 

01:08:22.710 --> 01:08:26.420
This discordance,
discourses, are part of a

01:08:26.420 --> 01:08:29.600
sovereign and transcendent
order,

01:08:29.600 --> 01:08:33.634
but he is a peace poet which is
truly scandalous because most

01:08:33.634 --> 01:08:35.420
poets,
except for Isaia,

01:08:35.420 --> 01:08:37.850
for instance who is a peace
poet--

01:08:37.850 --> 01:08:43.578
prophet, a prophet of peace,
with a vision of peace;

01:08:43.578 --> 01:08:47.840
Dante really has an irenic
vision.

01:08:47.840 --> 01:08:51.953
Most poets write about
victories, about wars,

01:08:51.953 --> 01:08:55.038
about armistices,
truces, epic;

01:08:55.038 --> 01:08:59.467
the epics in England or in
Italy, it's all about the

01:08:59.467 --> 01:09:01.640
clashes of armies,
etc.

01:09:01.640 --> 01:09:05.699
Not Dante, so that's really the
direct answer I can give to your

01:09:05.699 --> 01:09:06.408
question.
 

01:09:06.408 --> 01:09:09.492
Then you raise another issue
which I find a little bit--I

01:09:09.492 --> 01:09:13.180
would not want to go there but I
owe it to you to give an answer.

01:09:13.180 --> 01:09:16.578
Well, what about the peaceful
language of Francis?

01:09:16.578 --> 01:09:22.497
That seems to be such a great
idea because heresy and schisms

01:09:22.497 --> 01:09:25.701
and the question--
the relationship between

01:09:25.701 --> 01:09:28.420
Christians and Muslims has
always been one of wars,

01:09:28.420 --> 01:09:31.927
so heresy and war,
schism and war,

01:09:31.927 --> 01:09:38.305
so we can say that Dante seems
to be so radical in renouncing

01:09:38.305 --> 01:09:42.590
war and says,
look it's possible to harmonize

01:09:42.590 --> 01:09:46.641
relationship or at least
confront our differences with

01:09:46.641 --> 01:09:48.630
using a peace language.
 

01:09:48.630 --> 01:09:53.461
However, things are not as
simple as that and that's why I

01:09:53.461 --> 01:09:57.359
only mention it but I will not
go into that.

01:09:57.359 --> 01:09:58.510
We haven't got time for that.
 

01:09:58.510 --> 01:10:01.216
It's really a thought I am a
little developing,

01:10:01.216 --> 01:10:02.100
I must admit.
 

01:10:02.100 --> 01:10:05.399
The heresy is a question of
language.

01:10:05.399 --> 01:10:07.750
It's not just a question of
wars.

01:10:07.750 --> 01:10:13.769
So, there are wars that go on
in language and therefore they

01:10:13.769 --> 01:10:19.481
re-propose the very differences
and stubborn divisions of

01:10:19.481 --> 01:10:25.501
understanding that qualify and
describe both the schisms and

01:10:25.501 --> 01:10:27.439
the heresies.
 

01:10:27.439 --> 01:10:31.188
So, to say "peaceful
language,"

01:10:31.188 --> 01:10:34.750
it sounds also like another way
of--

01:10:34.750 --> 01:10:39.391
another route into potential
descent and tragedy,

01:10:39.391 --> 01:10:40.359
you see.
 

01:10:40.359 --> 01:10:45.434
But I am not going to go
anymore than give you as a kind

01:10:45.434 --> 01:10:50.786
of suspicion that I have about
my own claim that Dante is a

01:10:50.786 --> 01:10:52.170
peace poet.
 

